snippet.title: Java Mobile Game: Tetris (2008 Electronic Arts)
snippet.description:
Another implementation of the popular Tetris game for smartphones. It features a variety of game modes, beautiful graphics and good sound.

Please like this video and subscribe to my channel for more great retro content.
